Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Hear me, and rejoice. You have had the privilege of being saved by the Great Titan.... You may think this is suffering... no. It is salvation. Universal scales tip toward balance because of your sacrifice. Smile... [Corvus Glaive stabs one of the lingering Asgardians] for even in death, you have become Children of Thanos.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Looking out the large window we saw at the end of Thor

Name: Thor
Line: [Now being held by Thanos with one huge hand wrapping around his head; blood drools from his mouth] You talk too much.

Name: Thanos
Line: [To Loki] The Tesseract, or your brother's head. I assume you have a preference.

Name: Thor
Line: We don't have the Tesseract. It was destroyed on Asgard.

Name: Thor
Line: You really are the worst brother.

Name: Thanos
Line: Your optimism is misplaced, Asgardian.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Let him have his fun.

Name: Thanos
Line: That was a mistake.

Name: Thor
Line: NO!!! [After Thanos kills Heimdall] You're going to die for that!

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: [Shuts Thor's mouth with his telekinesis] Shh.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: [Kneels before Thanos, offering up the Tesseract] My humble personage… bows before your grandeur. No other being has ever had the might, nay the nobility, to wield not one, but two Infinity Stones. The universe lies within your grasp.

Name: Thanos
Line: There are two more Stones on Earth. Find them, my children, and bring them to me on Titan.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Unimpressed] If you consider failure experience.

Name: Thanos
Line: "Undying?" You should choose your words more carefully.

Name: Thor
Line: [Muffled] NO!

Name: Thanos
Line: [Walks over and drops Loki's body in front of Thor.] No resurrections this time.

Name: Thor
Line: No… Loki….

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Dressed in casual American clothes.] Seriously? You don't have any money?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: I'll tell the guys at the deli. [Wryly] Maybe they'll make you a metaphysical ham on rye.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Dollars?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Which is?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: What do you want?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Thanos is coming. He's coming...

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Sharing a look with Wong, and now fully in his mage attire] Who?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Slow down, slow down. I'm totally not kidding.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: [Laughing slightly and talking over him] You're totally rambling.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Also talking over her] No, I'm not.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Lost me.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Look, you know how you're having a dream, and in the dream you gotta pee?

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Okay, and then you're like, 'Oh my god, there's no bathroom, what am I gonna do?', 'Oh! Someone's watching,' ''m gonna go in my pants.'

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Right. And then you wake up, and in real life you actually have to pee.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yes.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Yeah. Everybody has that.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Right! That's the point I'm trying to make. Apropos of that, last night, I dreamt, we had a kid. So real. We named him after your eccentric uncle. Uh, what was his name?

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: [Nodding in understanding] Right.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Morgan! Morgan.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: So you woke up, and thought that we were...

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Expecting.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Yeah.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Becoming excited] Yes?

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: [Shaking her head] No.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I had a dream about it. It was so real.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: If you wanted to have a kid, you wouldn't have done that.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm glad you brought this up, 'cause it's nothing. It's just a housing unit for nano particles.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: It's not helping your case, OK?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No, no, it's an attachment, it's not a-

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: [Insistently] You don't need that.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I know. I had the surgery. I'm just trying to protect us. The future uses, and that's it. Just in case there's a monster in the closet, instead of, you know...

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Shirts?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You know me so well. You finish all my sentences.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: You should have shirts in your closet.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. You know what there should be? No more surprises. We're gonna have a nice dinner tonight. Show off this Harry Win-stone. Right? And we should have no more surprises. Ever. I should promise you.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Yes.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I will. [Tony kisses Pepper.]

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Tony Stark, I'm Doctor Stephen Strange. I need you to come with me. Oh, uh, congratulations on the wedding, by the way.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I'm sorry, you giving out tickets or something?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: We need your help. Look, it's not overselling to say that the fate of the universe is at stake.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And who's "we"?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Emerges from behind Doctor Strange] Hey, Tony.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Looking surprised] Bruce.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Pepper.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Hi.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You okay?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Each Stone lights up as Dr. Strange names them.] Space. Reality. Power. Soul. Mind. And Time.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Very attentive] Tell me his name again.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Thanos. He's a plague, Tony. He invades planets. He takes what he wants. He wipes out half the population. He sent Loki. The attack on New York. That's him.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Speaking to himself] This is it... What's our timeline?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: No telling. He has the Power and Space Stones, that already makes him the strongest creature in the whole universe. If he gets his hands, on all six Stones, Tony...

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: He can destroy life on a scale hitherto undreamt of.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Leans against a cauldron, stretching like he's about to go for a run.] Did you seriously just say "hitherto undreamt of"?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Are you seriously leaning on the Cauldron of the Cosmos?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Is that what this is.... ?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Looking offended] [Straightening himself] I'm going to allow that. If Thanos needs all six, why don't we just stick this one down the garbage disposal?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: No can do.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And I swore off dairy, but then, Ben & Jerry's named a flavor after me, so....

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Stark Raving Hazelnuts.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's not bad.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: A bit chalky.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: That's a thing?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Whatever. Point is

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Our oath to protect the Time Stone cannot change. This Stone may be the best chance we have against Thanos.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And still conversely, it may also be his best chance against us.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Well, if we don't do our jobs.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Slightly condescending] What is your job exactly, besides making balloon animals?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Completely calm] Protecting your reality, douchebag.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Okay, guys, could we table this discussion right now? The fact is that we have this Stone. We know where it is. Vision is out there somewhere with the Mind Stone, and we have to find him now.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Awkwardly] Yeah, that's the... thing.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: What do you mean?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Two weeks ago, Vision turned off his transponder. He's offline.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: What? Tony, you lost another super bot?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I didn't lose him. He's more than that. He's evolving.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Who could find Vision, then?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Quietly to himself] Shit. [To the other men in a normal tone] Probably Steve Rogers.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Sighing in exasperation] Oh, great.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Maybe. But... [Sighs]

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Missing the events of the Avengers' Civil War] Call him.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's not that easy. God, we haven't caught up in a spell, have we?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: No.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: The Avengers broke up. We're toast.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Rather surprised and slightly let-down] Broke up? Like a band? Like The Beatles?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Cap and I fell out hard. We're not on speaking terms.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Almost pleading] Tony, listen to me. Thor's gone. Thanos is coming. It doesn't matter who you're talking to or not.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Say, Doc, you wouldn't happen to be moving your hair, would you?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Looking up at his forelock fluttering] Not at the moment, no.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You okay?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Help him! Wong, Doc.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Go! Got it!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Putting on his sunglasses] F.R.I.D.A.Y., what am I looking at?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Hey! You might wanna put that Time Stone in your back pocket, Doc!

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Bands of spells are readied around his forearms] Might wanna use it.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Tapping his best friend in the seat in front of him] Ned, hey. I need you to cause a distraction.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: F.R.I.D.A.Y., evac anyone south of 43rd Street, notify first responders.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Hear me, and rejoice. You are about to die at the hands of the Children of Thanos. Be thankful, that your meaningless lives are now contributing to...

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Echoing the familiarly defiant 2008 Tony Stark] I'm sorry, Earth is closed today. You better pack it up and get outta here.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: [Looks at Doctor Strange] Stonekeeper... [Gestures to Tony] Does this chattering animal speak for you?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Certainly not. I speak for myself. [Magical shields are readied with his fists, stepping forward.] But you’re trespassing in this city and on this planet. [Wong emulates him.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It means get lost, Squidward!

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: He exhausts me.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Bring me the Stone.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Banner, you want a piece?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: No, not really, but when do I ever get what I want?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: That's right.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Been a while. Good to have you, buddy.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I just... I need to concentrate here for one second. Come on, come on, man.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Where's your guy?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I don't know. We've sort been havin' a thing.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: There's no time for a thing.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I know.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Points at the approaching Obsidian] That's the thing right there. Let's go.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Glances at Doctor Strange] Dude, you're embarrassing me in front of the wizards.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Tony, I'm sorry. [Stammers] Either I can't or he won't--

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's okay. Hey, stand down. [to Wong] Keep an eye on him. Thank you.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Damn it.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Where'd that come from?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: It's nano-tech. You like it? A little someth--

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Dr. Banner, if the rest of your green friend won't be joining us....

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Gotta get that stone outta here, now.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: It stays with me.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Exactly. Bye.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Rushing over to Iron Man] Tony, you okay? How we doing? Good? Bad?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Really, really good. Really good. Do you plan on helping out?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I'm trying. He won't come out.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Hammer. [Pushes Bruce out of the way.]

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Crawling out from under the branches. Desperate and confused] Come on, Hulk. What are you doing to me? [Starts slapping himself multiple times] Come out! Come out! Come out!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: What do you mean, "no"?!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, man. What's up, Mr. Stark?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Kid, where'd you come from?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Field trip to MoMA.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: What is this guy's problem, Mr. Stark?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: He's from space. He came here to steal a necklace from a wizard.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Your powers are quaint. You must be popular with children.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: It's a simple spell but quite unbreakable.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: [Vehemently] Then I'll take it off your corpse.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: You'll find... removing a dead man's spell... troublesome.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: You'll only wish you were dead. [Doctor Strange falls unconscious and to the ground; Maw raises a portion of street pavement to use as a carrier, but the Cloak of Levitation works its master loose of the cable spiral and flies Doctor Strange away.] NO!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Still fighting Cull Obsidian, as Doctor Strange passes through the park.] Kid, that's the wizard. Get on it.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: On it!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Untangles himself] Not cool!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Uhhh, Mr. Stark? I'm being beamed up!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Hang on, kid. [Cull Obsidian's hammer doubles as a claw, pinning Iron Man to the ground and shorting his suit. As Obsidian jumps towards Iron Man, blades ready to end this fight, he is sent through a portal instead. The alien turns and leaps to return the same way, but Wong closes it rapidly -- only Obsidian's severed hand makes it back to the park. Bruce kicks the hand away with a noise of disgust.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Iron Man shakes himself free of the Dwarf's weapon, now powerless.] Wong, you're invited to my wedding. [Iron Man begins to fly towards the large ship] Give me a little juice, F.R.I.D.A.Y. [Iron Man's foot thrusters morph together into a single larger jet and increase his speed considerably.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Still in pursuit of the ship and his protege.] Unlock 17-A. [A pod launches from the upstate Avengers headquarters and curves up to the accelerating circular ship.] Pete, you gotta let go. I'm gonna catch you.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: But you said save the wizard! [Spider-Man, gasping from lack of oxygen, pulls off his mask] I can't breathe!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You're too high up. You're running out of air.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah! That makes sense.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Mr. Stark, it smells like a new car in here!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Happy trails, kid. F.R.I.D.A.Y, send him home.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: OH, COME ON!

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: [Sounding heavily worried] Tony? Oh, my God. Are you all right? What's going on?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, I'm fine. I just think we might have to push our 8

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Why?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [While looking at the ship around him] Just 'cause I'll... probably not make it back for a while.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Tell me you're not on that ship.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: God, no. Please tell me you're not on that ship.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Honey, I'm sorry. I'm sorry, I don't know what to say.

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Come back here, Tony. I swear to God….

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Pep….

Name: Pepper Potts
Line: Come back here right now! Come back!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Oh my God! [Looks at the rapidly-receding planet behind him] I should have stayed on the bus....

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Where you going?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Holding Rogers' cell phone] I'm gonna make a call.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Chair-dancing to the song] Sing it, Drax!

Name: Rocket
Line: [Yawns] Why are we doing this again?

Name: Gamora
Line: [Annoyed] It's a distress signal, Rocket. Someone could be dying.

Name: Rocket
Line: I get that, but why are we doing it?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: 'Cause we're nice. And maybe whoever it is will give us a little cheddar cheese [Quill rubs his thumb against his other fingers] for our help.

Name: Gamora
Line: [Waves her index finger at Quill] Which isn't the point.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Points back at Gamora] Which isn't the point... I mean… if he doesn't pony up….

Name: Drax
Line: We'll take his ship.

Name: Rocket
Line: Exactly!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: B-b-b-bingo!

Name: Mantis
Line: [Reading her console] We are arriving.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: All right, Guardians. Don't forget, this might be dangerous, so let's put on our mean faces. [Groot rolls his eyes as Mantis makes a snarl. Groot's handheld Terran-vintage video game beeps.] Groot, put that thing away. Now. I don't wanna tell you again. [Game continues beeping] Groot.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Whoa!

Name: Rocket
Line: Language!

Name: Gamora
Line: Hey!

Name: Drax
Line: Wow.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: You got some acorns on you, kid.

Name: Rocket
Line: Ever since you got a little sap, you're a total d-hole. Keep it up, and I'm gonna SMASH THAT THING TO PIECES!

Name: Mantis
Line: What happened?

Name: Rocket
Line: Looks like we're not getting paid.

Name: Rocket
Line: [Waving his hands] Wipers! Wipers! Get it off!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: How the hell is this dude still alive?

Name: Drax
Line: [Sounding awed] He is not a dude. You're a dude. This... this is a man. A handsome, muscular man.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [A little dented] I'm muscular.

Name: Rocket
Line: Who are you kidding, Quill? You're one sandwich away from fat.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Yeah, right.

Name: Drax
Line: It's true. You have gained a little weight…. [Drax motions to his chin and belly.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: What? Gamora, do you think I'm…

Name: Mantis
Line: He is anxious. Angry. He feels tremendous loss and guilt.

Name: Drax
Line: It's like a pirate had a baby with an angel.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Wow. This is a real wake-up call for me. Okay. I'm gonna get a Bow-flex. I'm gonna commit. I'm gonna get some dumbbells.

Name: Rocket
Line: You know you can't eat dumbbells, right?

Name: Gamora
Line: [Reaches Drax's side and picks up Thor's left arm, stroking his triceps] It's like his muscles are made of Cotati metal fibers.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Snidely to Gamora] Stop massaging his muscles. [Gamora, annoyed, drops the arm with a thump; quietly to Mantis] Wake him up.

Name: Mantis
Line: [Places hand on Thor's forehead] Wake.

Name: Thor
Line: Who the hell are you guys?

Name: Gamora
Line: The entire time I knew Thanos, he only ever had one goal

Name: Drax
Line: Including my own.

Name: Gamora
Line: If he gets all six Infinity Stones, he can do it with the snap of his fingers, like this. [She snaps her fingers.]

Name: Thor
Line: You seem to know a great deal about Thanos.

Name: Drax
Line: Gamora... is the daughter of Thanos.

Name: Thor
Line: Your father killed my brother. [Thor stands and strides towards Gamora aggressively.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Oh, boy. Stepfather. Technically, she hates him as much as you do. [Thor softens a bit.]

Name: Thor
Line: Families can be tough. [He claps a hand on Gamora's shoulder] Before my father died, he told me I had a half-sister... that he imprisoned in Hel. Then she returned home, and stabbed me in the eye, so... I had to kill her. It's life, isn't it, I guess. Goes round and round and... I feel your pain.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: And I feel your pain, as well. I mean it's not a competition, but I've been through a lot. My father killed my mother, then I had to kill my father. And that was hard. Probably even harder than having to kill a sister. Plus, I, came out of it with both of my eyes--

Name: Thor
Line: [Not paying attention as he stares at his soup spoon] I need a hammer, not a spoon…. (He attempts to fiddle with machinery) How do I open this thing? Is there some sort of a four-digit code maybe… maybe a birth date or something….

Name: Peter Quill
Line: What are you doing?

Name: Thor
Line: Taking your pod.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Clears his throat then deepens his voice] No, you're not! [Mimics Thor’s accent] You'll not, be taking our pod today, sir.

Name: Rocket
Line: Quill. Are you making your voice deeper?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: No.

Name: Drax
Line: You are. You're imitating the god-man. It's weird.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: No I'm not.

Name: Mantis
Line: [Gasp] He just did it again!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: This is my voice!

Name: Thor
Line: [Steps closer to Quill] Are you mocking me?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Are you mocking me?

Name: Thor
Line: Stop it. You did it again.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: He's trying to copy me.

Name: Thor
Line: Would you stop doing that? He's doing it first.

Name: Gamora
Line: Enough! We need to stop Thanos. Which means we need to find out where he's going next.

Name: Thor
Line: Knowhere.

Name: Mantis
Line: He must be going somewhere.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Voice now normal] No. Knowhere? It's a place. We've been there. It sucks. Excuse me, that's our food. [To Thor as he rummages through their food stores.]

Name: Thor
Line: Not anymore.

Name: Gamora
Line: Thor… why would he go to Knowhere?

Name: Thor
Line: Because for years, the Reality Stone has been safely stored, there with a man we call the Collector.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: If it's with the Collector, then it's not safe. Only an idiot would give that man a stone.

Name: Thor
Line: Or a genius.

Name: Gamora
Line: [To Thor] How do you know he's not going for one of the other Stones?

Name: Thor
Line: There's six stones out there. [Finishes rummaging and steps in front of Gamora] Thanos already has the Power Stone because he stole it last week, when he decimated Xandar. He stole the Space Stone from me when he destroyed my ship and slaughtered half my people. The Time and Mind Stones are safe on Earth. They're with the Avengers.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: The 'Avengers'?

Name: Thor
Line: [By way of explanation.] Earth's Mightiest Heroes.

Name: Mantis
Line: Like Kevin Bacon?

Name: Thor
Line: [Pause] He may be on the team. I don't know. Haven't been there in a while. As for the Soul Stone, well, no one's ever seen that. No one even knows where it is. Therefore, Thanos can't get it. Therefore, he's going to Knowhere. Hence, he'll be getting the Reality Stone. You're welcome.

Name: Gamora
Line: Then we have to go to Knowhere now.

Name: Thor
Line: Wrong! Where we have to go, is Nivadellir.

Name: Drax
Line: That's a made up word.

Name: Thor
Line: All words are made up.

Name: Rocket
Line: Hold up, Nidavellir is real? [Climbing on to the table] Seriously? I mean, that place is a legend. [Increasingly gleeful] They make the most powerful, horrific weapons to ever torment the Universe. I would very much like to go there, please.

Name: Thor
Line: The rabbit is correct, and clearly the smartest among you.

Name: Rocket
Line: Rabbit?

Name: Thor
Line: Only Eitri the dwarf king can make me the weapon I need. [To Rocket] I assume you're the captain, sir?

Name: Rocket
Line: You're very perceptive.

Name: Thor
Line: You seem like a noble leader. Will you join me on my quest to Nidavellir?

Name: Rocket
Line: Lemme just ask the captain. Oh, wait a second, it's me! Yeah, I'll go.

Name: Thor
Line: Wonderful.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Except for that I'm the captain.

Name: Thor
Line: Quiet!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: That's my backpack.

Name: Rocket
Line: Go sit down.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [To Thor] Look, this is my ship. And I'm not goin' to… [gropes for "Nidavellir"] Wait, what kind of weapon are we talking about here?

Name: Thor
Line: The Thanos killing kind.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Don't you think that we should all have a weapon like that?

Name: Thor
Line: No. You simply lack the strength to wield them. Your bodies will crumble as your minds collapse into the madness.

Name: Rocket
Line: Is it weird that I wanna do it even more now?

Name: Thor
Line: A little bit. Yeah.

Name: Gamora
Line: If we don't go to Knowhere and Thanos retrieves another stone, he'll be too powerful to stop.

Name: Thor
Line: He already is.

Name: Rocket
Line: I got it figured out. We got two ships, and a large assortment of morons. So me and Groot will go with the pirate-angel here, and the morons will go to Knowhere to try and stop Thanos. Cool? Cool.

Name: Thor
Line: So cool. [Smiles a big grin.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [To Rocket] For the record… I know that you're only going with him because it's where Thanos isn't.

Name: Rocket
Line: You know, you shouldn't talk that way to your captain, Quill. [As he enters the pod] Come on, Groot. Put that game down, you'll rot your brain.

Name: Thor
Line: I bid you farewell and good luck, morons. Bye.

Name: Vision
Line: [Gasps and holds his hand to the Mind Stone in pain.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vis? Is it the stone again?

Name: Vision
Line: It's as if it's speaking to me.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: What does it say?

Name: Vision
Line: I don't... I don't know. But something...

Name: Vision
Line: Tell me what you feel.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I just feel you.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: So there's a 10 AM to Glasgow to give us more time together before you went back.

Name: Vision
Line: What if I miss that train?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: There is an 11.

Name: Vision
Line: What if I missed all the trains? What if this time, I didn't go back?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You gave Stark your word.

Name: Vision
Line: I'd rather give it to you.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: There are people who are expecting me too, you know. We both made promises.

Name: Vision
Line: Not to each other. [He puts his hands on her shoulders] Wanda… for two years, we've stolen these moments, trying to see if this could work. And... I don't know. [Stammers] You know what, I'm just gonna speak for myself -- I, I... I think...

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: It works.

Name: Vision
Line: It works.

Name: Vision
Line: Then stay. Stay with me.

Name: Vision
Line: [Suddenly very uncertain] Or not. If I'm overstepping…

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [Fearful] What are they?

Name: Vision
Line: What the stone was warning me about. [He kisses her hand] I have to go.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: No, Vision. Vision, if that's true… then maybe going isn't the best idea.

Name: Vision
Line: Wanda, I… [Corvus Glaive appears suddenly behind Vision, stabbing him through the back. Vision screams, loses his glamour to return to his green, red and gold appearance, and is thrown down into the street.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vision! [She circles her hands, gathering up energy for a counterattack when Proxima Midnight blasts her from behind, knocking the Scarlet Witch across the street and through a bistro's window.]

Name: Vision
Line: The blade. It stopped me from phasing.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Is that even possible?

Name: Vision
Line: It isn't supposed to be. [His voice distorts electronically] My systems are failing. [The Scarlet Witch gestures over his gaping wound, using her magic to knit him back together. Vision continues in a gasping, wry tone] I'm beginning to think... we should have stayed in bed.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Vis!

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Hands off.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [Hushed voice, pleading.] Come on. Come on. Come on, you gotta get up. You gotta get up. Come on. Hey. Hey. We have to go.

Name: Vision
Line: Please. Please leave.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You asked me to stay.... I'm staying.

Name: Vision
Line: Please.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Get up.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [Coolly] We don't wanna kill you. But we will.

Name: Vision
Line: [Electricity shimmers over his surface, and his voice distorts] Thank you, Captain.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Nods] Let's get you on the jet.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [Closing the doors to the Quinjet, while addressing Wanda] I thought we had a deal. Stay close, check in. Don't take any chances.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I'm sorry. We just wanted time.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Home.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Zehobereians…

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Zen-Whoberis... Choose a side, or die.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: One side is a revelation. The other, an honor known only to a few.

Name: Thanos
Line: What's wrong, little one?

Name: Thanos
Line: [Kneels down to Gamora] What's your name?

Name: Thanos
Line: You're quite the fighter, Gamora. Come. Let me help you. [Thanos offers his hand; she wraps her little fingers around one massive finger, and he leads her to a pavilion, where he crouches to her eye level again and produces a small -- for him -- red-jeweled handle. Pressing the switch, razor-sharp blades pop out both ends.] Look. Pretty, isn't it? Perfectly balanced. As all things should be. Too much to one side, or the other… [He balances it on one finger, overbalances it purposefully and catches it.] Here. You try.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Now go in peace, and meet your Maker.

Name: Thanos
Line: Concentrate. There! You've got it.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Gamora. Do you know if these grenades are the "blow off your junk" kind or the gas kind? 'Cause I was thinking I might hang a couple on my belt right here. But I don't want to--

Name: Gamora
Line: I need to ask a favor.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Yeah, sure.

Name: Gamora
Line: One way or another, the path that we're on leads to Thanos.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Which is what the grenades are for. [Gamora silences him with a look.] I'm sorry. What's the favor?

Name: Gamora
Line: If things go wrong… If Thanos gets me… I want you to promise me… you'll kill me.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [A beat. Confusion.] What?

Name: Gamora
Line: I know something he doesn't. If he finds out… the entire Universe could be at risk.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: What do you know?

Name: Gamora
Line: If I tell you, you'd know, too.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: If it's so important, shouldn't I?

Name: Gamora
Line: Only if you wanna die.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Why does somebody always have to die in this scenario?

Name: Gamora
Line: Just… trust me. And possibly, kill me.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: I mean, I'd like to. I really would… [Gamora silences him by covering his mouth with her hand.]

Name: Gamora
Line: Swear to me. Swear to me on your mother.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [A beat. One that rests with him significantly.] Okay.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Dude. How long have you been standing there?

Name: Drax
Line: An hour.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: An hour? Are you serious?

Name: Drax
Line: I've mastered the ability of standing so incredibly still... that I become invisible to the eye... watch.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: You're eating a zarg-nut.

Name: Drax
Line: But my movement... was so slow... that it's imperceptible.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Mmm, no. [Quill and Gamora shake their heads.]

Name: Drax
Line: I'm sure I'm invisible.

Name: Mantis
Line: Hi, Drax.

Name: Drax
Line: [Knowing when he is beat] Damn it.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: This place looks deserted.

Name: Drax
Line: I'm reading movement from the third quadrant.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Yep. I'm picking that up, too. Let's put it down right here.

Name: Thanos
Line: Everyone in the Galaxy knows you'd sell your own brother if you thought it would add the slightest trinket to your pathetic collection.

Name: Thanos
Line: I know you have the Reality Stone, Tivan. Giving it to me will spare you a great deal of suffering. [Thanos places a heavy boot on the middle of the Collector's chest and presses.]

Name: Thanos
Line: I imagine it's like breathing for you.

Name: Thanos
Line: So you do understand. Not even you would surrender something so precious.

Name: Thanos
Line: Then you're more of a fool than I took you for. Last chance, charlatan. Where's the Stone?

Name: Drax
Line: Today...

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Grasping the danger] Drax. Drax.

Name: Drax
Line: ...He pays for the deaths of my wife and daughter.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Drax, waaaaait! [Drax draws his long dagger from his leg scabbard.] Not yet, not yet, not yet. [Drax gives him a look and heads towards Thanos. Quill hurries as quietly as possible to catch up.] Drax, Drax, Drax. He doesn't have the Stone yet. We get it, and then we can stop him. We have to get the Stone first. Yeah.

Name: Drax
Line: No. No. For Ovette. For Camaria.

Name: Mantis
Line: Sleeeep. [Drax is knocked out, his falling body causing a loud crash. Everybody ducks.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Okay. Gamora, Mantis, you go right. I'm... [Gamora moves towards Thanos] The other right!

Name: Thanos
Line: Why? [He falls down] Why you? Daughter… [He holds his hand out to her, blood pooling out from his neck wound, before collapsing completely. Gamora breaks down, sobbing.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Surprised] That was quick.

Name: Thanos
Line: Is it sadness I sense in you, daughter? In my heart, I knew you still cared. But one ever knows for sure. Reality is often disappointing.

Name: Thanos
Line: That is, it was. Now… reality can be whatever I want.

Name: Gamora
Line: [Her face still wet, but no longer crying] You knew I'd come.

Name: Thanos
Line: I counted on it. There's something we need to discuss, little one.

Name: Drax
Line: Thanos!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Moving in, his blaster pointed right at Thanos] Let her go, Grimace!

Name: Gamora
Line: Peter…

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [To Gamora] I told you to go right.

Name: Gamora
Line: Now? Really?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: You let her go!

Name: Thanos
Line: Ah, the boyfriend.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: I like to think of myself more as a Titan-killing long-term booty call. Let her go.

Name: Gamora
Line: Peter…

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Or I'm gonna blow that nut sack of a chin right off your face!

Name: Gamora
Line: Not him.

Name: Gamora
Line: You promised! You promised.

Name: Thanos
Line: Oh, daughter. You expect too much from him. [to Quill] She's asked, hasn't she? Do it. [There is a very tense and unpleasant pause. Thanos rolls his head and shoves Gamora towards Quill’s gun, egging him on.] DO IT!!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Tearing up] I told you to go right.

Name: Gamora
Line: I love you, more than anything.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: I love you, too.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Genuinely sincere] I like you.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Satellites lost him somewhere over Edinburgh.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: You know they're only criminals because you've chosen to call them that, right, sir?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: If it weren't for those Accords, Vision would've been right here.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: [Sounding a little bitter] That's right. And I'm pretty sure I've paid for that. [We get a good look at his leg braces]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Not anymore.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Mr. Secretary.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: You could use some of that right now.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I'm not looking for forgiveness. And I'm way past asking for permission. Earth just lost her best defender. So we're here to fight. [Steve takes a step forward, looking right at Ross] And if you wanna stand in our way... we'll fight you, too.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: All over it. [Swipes off hologram; the computer beeps twice] That's a court-martial. It's great to see you, Cap.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Hugging Rhodes] You too, Rhodey. [Natasha gets her own embrace.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Well. You guys really look like crap. Must've been a rough couple of years.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Uh, I think you look great. [Rhodes and Natasha long round to see Bruce walking in from the opposite end of the room.] Uh... heh... Yeah. I'm back.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Hi, Bruce.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Nat.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: So we gotta assume they're coming back, right?

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: And they can clearly find us.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: We need all hands on deck. Where's Clint?

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: After the whole Accords situation, he and Scott took a deal. It was too tough on their families, they're on house arrest.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Who's Scott?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Ant-Man.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: There's an Ant-Man and a Spider-Man? Okay, look… Thanos has the biggest army in the universe. And he is not gonna stop until he... he gets... Vision's Stone.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Well then, we have to protect it.

Name: Vision
Line: No, we have to destroy it. I've been giving a good deal of thought to this entity in my head, about its nature. But also, its composition. I think if it were exposed to a sufficiently powerful energy source, something, very similar to its own signature, perhaps… its molecular integrity could fail. [Vision addresses Wanda as he nears her.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: And you, with it. We're not having this conversation.

Name: Vision
Line: Eliminating the stone is the only way to be certain that Thanos can't get it.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: That's too high a price.

Name: Vision
Line: [Takes her face gently in both hands] Only you have the power to pay it. [Wanda walks away, distressed] Thanos threatens half the Universe. One life cannot stand in the way of defeating him.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Eyes diverted down] But it should. [Looks up at Vision] We don't trade lives, Vision.

Name: Vision
Line: [Walking toward Steve] Captain, 70 years ago, you laid down your life to save how many millions of people. Tell me, why is this any different?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Because you might have a choice. Your mind is made up of a complex construct of overlays. J.A.R.V.I.S., Ultron, Tony, me, the Stone. All of them mixed together. All of them learning from one another.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: You're saying Vision isn't just the stone?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I'm saying that if we take out the stone, there's still a whole lot of Vision left. Perhaps the best parts.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Can we do that?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Not me. Not here.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: You better find someone, and somewhere fast. Ross isn't exactly just gonna let you guys have your old rooms back.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: I know somewhere.

Name: T'Challa
Line: And the Border Tribe?

Name: T'Challa
Line: Send word to the Jabari as well. M'Baku likes a good fight.

Name: T'Challa
Line: This one may be tired of war. [James "Bucky" Buchanan Barnes is seen at a small distance throwing a bag from a pile on the ground onto a partly-filled cart, while two village children watch] But the White Wolf has rested long enough.

Name: T'Challa
Line: On its way.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: In all the time I've served Thanos, I've never failed him. If I were to reach our rendezvous on Titan with the Time Stone still attached to your vaguely irritating person, there would be... judgement. [The needles start to contact Dr. Strange's face, causing an obviously painful whitish subcutaneous glow at each touch] Give me... the stone.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Wow you're a seriously loyal piece of outerwear, aren't you?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yeah, uh, speaking of loyalty....

Name: Tony Stark
Line: What the--

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I know what you're gonna say.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You should not be here.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I was gonna go home--

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I don't wanna hear it.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: But it was such a long way down and I just thought about you on the way...

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And now I gotta hear it.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: ...And I kinda stuck to the side of the ship. And this suit is ridiculously intuitive, by the way. So if anything, it's kinda your fault that I'm here.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Seriously] What did you just say?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I take that back. And now I'm here in space.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. [Tony crosses to stand right in front of Peter] Right where I don't want you to be. This isn't Coney Island. This isn't a field trip. It's a one-way ticket. You hear me? Don't pretend like you thought this through. You could not have possibly thought this through.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No. I did think this through.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You could not have possibly thought this through.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It's just .. you can't be a friendly neighborhood Spider-Man if there's no neighborhood. [He waits for Tony's reaction] Okay. That didn't really make any sense, but you know what I'm trying to say.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Breaths shakily] Come on. We got a situation. [He leads Peter over to a viewpoint on the torture below. Peter crouches to study the situation, the Cloak leaning over his shoulder.] See him down there? He's in trouble. What's your plan? Go.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Um. Okay, okay... uh... [Peter and the Cloak pop back upright] Okay. Did you ever see this really old movie, Aliens?

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: Painful aren't they? They were originally designed for microsurgery. And any one of them...

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: ...Could end your friend's life in an instant.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I gotta tell you, he's not really my friend. Saving his life is more a professional courtesy.

Name: Ebony Maw
Line: [Walks slowly towards Iron Man, beckoning very large, very solid metal objects to float behind him] You've saved nothing. Your powers are inconsequential compared to mine.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, but the kid's seen more movies.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yes! Wait what are those?!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, we haven't officially met. [He offers the Cape his hand to shake. It ignores his offer and continues to Dr. Strange.] Cool.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: We've gotta turn this ship around.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah. Now he wants to run. Great plan.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: No, I want to protect the stone.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Irritably] And I want you to thank me now. Go ahead, I'm listening.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: For what? Nearly blasting me into space?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Who just saved your magical ass? Me.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: I seriously don't know how you fit your head into that helmet.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Admit it. You should have ducked out when I told you to. I tried to bench you. You refused.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Unlike everyone else in your life, I don't work for you.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: And due to that fact, we're now in a flying doughnut billions of miles away from Earth with no backup.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Raises his hand] I'm backup.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: No. You're a stowaway. [Waggles a finger between himself and Dr. Strange] The adults are talking.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: I'm sorry, I'm confused as to the relationship here. Wh-- what is he, your ward?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: No. I'm Peter, by the way.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Dr. Strange.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Oh, we're using our made-up names. Um... I'm Spider-Man, then.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: This ship is self-correcting its course. Thing's on autopilot.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Walks closer to Tony] Can we control it? Fly us home? [Tony is lost in bad memories and does not respond right away.] Stark?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Can you get us home?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah I heard you. I'm thinking... I'm not so sure we should.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Under no circumstance can we bring the Time Stone to Thanos. I don't think you quite understand what's at stake here.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Stalks over to Strange] No. It's you who doesn't understand, that Thanos has been inside my head for six years since he sent an army to New York and now he's back! And I don't know what to do. So I'm not so sure if it's a better plan to fight him on our turf or his but you saw what they did, what they can do. At least on his turf, he's not expecting it. So I say we take the fight to him. Doctor. Do you concur?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Pauses] Alright, Stark. We go to him. But you have to understand... if it comes to saving you or the kid or the Time Stone... I will not hesitate to let either of you die. I can't, because the fate of the universe depends on it.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Nice. Good. Moral compass. We're straight. [Stepping over to Peter, he formally taps each of Peter's shoulders with the edge of his hand, dubbing him as is done at a knighting.] Alright, kid. You're an Avenger now. [He doesn't look at him as he says those words, knowing well what he is signing him up for.]

Name: Thanos
Line: I thought you might be hungry.

Name: Gamora
Line: I always hated that chair.

Name: Thanos
Line: So I've been told. Even so. I'd hoped you'd sit on it one day.

Name: Gamora
Line: I hated this room. This ship. I hated my life.

Name: Thanos
Line: You told me that too. [Thanos mounts two of the four steps to his throne, turns, and sits on the second from the top.] Every day. For almost twenty years.

Name: Gamora
Line: I was a child when you took me.

Name: Thanos
Line: I saved you.

Name: Gamora
Line: No. No. We were happy on my home planet.

Name: Thanos
Line: Going to bed hungry, scrounging for scraps. Your planet was on the brink of collapse. I'm the one who stopped that. Do you know what's happened since then? The children born have known nothing but full bellies and clear skies. It's a paradise.

Name: Gamora
Line: Because you murdered half the planet.

Name: Thanos
Line: A small price to pay for salvation.

Name: Gamora
Line: You're insane.

Name: Thanos
Line: Little one, it's a simple calculus. This universe is finite, its resources finite. If life is left unchecked, life will cease to exist. It needs correction.

Name: Gamora
Line: You don't know that!

Name: Thanos
Line: [Scowls as his egotistical narcissism prevents him from fully listening to her] I'm the only one who knows that. At least, I'm the only one with the will to act on it. [He stands again and walks back to Gamora] For a time... you had that same will... as you fought by my side. Daughter.

Name: Gamora
Line: I'm not your daughter. Everything I hate about myself you taught me.

Name: Thanos
Line: And in doing so, made you the fiercest woman in the galaxy. That's why I trusted you to find the Soul Stone.

Name: Gamora
Line: I'm sorry I disappointed you.

Name: Thanos
Line: I am disappointed. But not because you didn't find it. [Leans down to put their heads at a level, whispering fiercely] But because you did. [Looks at her] And you lied.

Name: Gamora
Line: Nebula.

Name: Gamora
Line: Don't do this.

Name: Thanos
Line: Some time ago, your sister snuck aboard this ship to kill me.

Name: Gamora
Line: Please don't do this.

Name: Thanos
Line: And very nearly succeeded. So I brought her here. To talk.

Name: Gamora
Line: Stop. Stop it. [She puts her hands on the gauntlet, pulling it down] I swear to you on my life. I never found the Soul Stone.

Name: Thanos
Line: [To Gamora, walking around behind her] You're strong. Me. You're generous. Me. But I never taught you to lie. That's why you're so bad at it. [His voice drips with disgust] Where is the Soul Stone? [He raises his gauntlet next to Gamora's face. Nebula shakes her head, expression terrified, to encourage her sister's silence but when Gamora does not answer, Thanos clenches the gauntlet again, brow furrowed at his adopted daughter as the Power and Space Stones are reactivated. Gamora grimaces in shared pain at her sister's screams, growing louder as Thanos increases the pressure.]

Name: Gamora
Line: Vormir! [Thanos unclenches his hand, and Nebula gasps in air as her parts snap back almost into place. Gamora goes to her and caresses her face.] The Stone is on Vormir.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Satisfied.] Show me.

Name: Rocket
Line: Tinkle in the cup. We're not looking. What's there to see? What's a twig? Everybody's seen a twig.

Name: Thor
Line: [While looking out the rear portholes] Tree, pour what's in the cup out in space, and go in the cup again.

Name: Rocket
Line: You speak Groot?

Name: Thor
Line: Yes, they taught it on Asgard. It was an elective.

Name: Thor
Line: You'll know when we're there. Nivadellir's forge harnesses the power of a blazing neutron star. [Nostalgically] It's the birth place of my hammer. It's truly awesome.

Name: Rocket
Line: [To himself] Okay, time to be the captain. [Walks to a console near by Thor, presses two buttons] So, dead brother, huh? Yeah, that can be annoying.

Name: Thor
Line: Well, he's been dead before, but this time I think it really might be true.

Name: Rocket
Line: And you said your sister and your dad?

Name: Thor
Line: Both dead.

Name: Rocket
Line: Still got a mom, though?

Name: Thor
Line: Killed by a dark elf.

Name: Rocket
Line: A best friend?

Name: Thor
Line: Stabbed through the heart.

Name: Rocket
Line: Are you sure you're up to this particular murder mission?

Name: Thor
Line: [Smiling widely but also trying to convince himself] Absolutely. Rage, vengeance, anger, loss, regret... they're all tremendous motivators. They really clear the mind. So I'm good to go.

Name: Rocket
Line: Yeah, but this Thanos we're talking about... he's the toughest there is.

Name: Thor
Line: Well, he's never fought me.

Name: Rocket
Line: Yeah, he has!

Name: Thor
Line: He's never fought me twice. And I'm getting a new hammer, don't forget.

Name: Rocket
Line: Better be some hammer.

Name: Thor
Line: You know, I'm 1,500 years old. I've killed twice as many enemies as that, and every one would have rather killed me, but none succeeded. I'm only alive because fate wants me alive. Thanos is the latest in a long line of bastards and he will be the latest to feel my vengeance. Fate wills it so.

Name: Rocket
Line: And what if you're wrong?

Name: Thor
Line: If I'm wrong then... what more could I lose?

Name: Rocket
Line: [Under his breath] I could lose a lot. Me personally. I could lose a lot. [Rocket takes an eyeball from somewhere on his person] Okay. If fate does want you to kill that crapsack... you're gonna need more than one stupid eyeball. [He gives Thor the eyeball.]

Name: Thor
Line: What's this?

Name: Rocket
Line: What's it look like? Some jerk lost a bet with me on on Contraxia.

Name: Thor
Line: He gave you his eye?

Name: Rocket
Line: He gave me 100 credits. I snuck in later that night and stole his eye.

Name: Thor
Line: Thank you, sweet rabbit.

Name: Rocket
Line: Hmm. Huh? Oh. I would've washed that. The only way I could sneak it off Contraxia was up my...[beeping] Hey, we're here!

Name: Thor
Line: [Smacking his palm against the side of his head to get the eye calibrated] I don't think this thing works. Everything seems dark.

Name: Rocket
Line: It ain't the eye.

Name: Thor
Line: Something's wrong. The star's gone out. And the rings are frozen.

Name: Rocket
Line: I hope these dwarves are better at forging than they are cleaning. Maybe they realized they live in a junk pile in the middle of space.

Name: Thor
Line: This forge hasn't gone dark in centuries....

Name: Rocket
Line: [Pauses, looking at a pedestal] You said Thanos had a gauntlet, right?

Name: Thor
Line: Yes. Why?

Name: Rocket
Line: Look anything like that? [In fact, it looks exactly like that]

Name: Thor
Line: [Urgently] Go back to the pod.

Name: Thor
Line: Eitri, wait! Stop!

Name: Eitri
Line: Thor?

Name: Thor
Line: What happened here?

Name: Eitri
Line: You were supposed to protect us. Asgard was supposed to protect us!

Name: Thor
Line: Asgard is destroyed. [Thor scrambles to his feet and points. Eitri stop his attack on Thor. He now believes Thanos had destroyed Asgard and leaving him in a similar survivor role like Eitri himself.] Eitri, the glove. What did you do?

Name: Eitri
Line: [He walks brokenly across the space to sit heavily, leaning against an ore skip. Rocket and Groot get to their feet, the sapling checking his game.] 300 dwarves lived on this ring. I thought if I did what he asked, they'd be safe. I made what he wanted. A device capable of harnessing the power of the stones. Then he killed everyone anyway. All except me. 'Your life is yours,' he said. 'But your hands are mine alone.' [He holds up his immobile metal fists, encased in hardened molten metal.]

Name: Thor
Line: Eitri, this isn't about your hands. Every weapon you've ever designed

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [To Tony] Hey, what's going on?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: I think we're here.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: I don't think this rig has a self-park function. [Urgently] Get your hand into this steering gimbal. Close those around it. You understand?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Yep, got it.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: This was meant for one big guy, so we gotta to move at the same time.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay. Okay. Ready.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: We might wanna turn. Turn! Turn! Turn!!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [To Doctor Strange] You alright? [Panting] That was close. I owe you one.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Let me just say, if aliens wind up implanting eggs in my chest or something, and I eat one of you, I'm sorry.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [While pointing at Peter] I don't wanna hear another single pop culture out of you for the rest of the trip. You understand?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: I'm trying to say that... something is coming.

Name: Drax
Line: [Yelling] THANOS!!!! [He flings a blade at Doctor Strange, who neatly deflects it with a mystical shield, and in return sends the Cloak of Levitation at Drax's face, half-smothering him and throwing him to the floor. Star-Lord and Iron Man have a brief dogfight until a magnetic disc pins Iron Man face-first to a structure.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Crawling backwards frantically from an anxious-looking Mantis] AH! Whoawhoawhoawhoa! PLEASE DON'T PUT YOUR EGGS IN ME!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Stay down, clown!

Name: Drax
Line: [Struggling with the Cloak of Levitation] Die, blanket of death!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Alright, everybody, stay where you are... chill the F out. [Star-Lord powers off his helmet] I'm gonna ask you this one time. Where's Gamora?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [De-helmeting] Yeah, I'll do you one better. Who's Gamora?

Name: Drax
Line: I'll do you one better. Why is Gamora?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Tell me where the girl is, or I swear to you, I'm gonna French-fry this little freak.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Let's do it! You shoot my guy, I blast him. Let's go! [Tony extends his nano-tech cannon, looking uncannily like an electric shark about to eat Drax's face.]

Name: Drax
Line: Do it, Quill! I can take it.

Name: Mantis
Line: No, he can't take it!

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Completely deadpan] She's right. You can't.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Oh yeah? You don't wanna tell me where she is? That's fine. I'll kill all three of you and beat it out of Thanos myself. [To Spider-Man] Starting with you.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Wait, what. Thanos? [Trying to inject clarity and sanity into the situation] Alright, let me ask you this one time

Name: Peter Quill
Line: What master do I serve? What am I supposed to say? "Jesus"?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Getting it] You're from Earth?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: I'm not from Earth. I'm from Missouri.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, that's on Earth, dip-shit. What are you hassling us for?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Sounding slightly crushed] So, you're not with Thanos?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Indignantly] With Thanos?! No, I'm here to kill Thanos! He took my girl- Wai- who are you?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [De-helmets] We're the Avengers, man.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Oh.

Name: Mantis
Line: You're the ones Thor told us about!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You know Thor!?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Yeah. Tall guy, not that good-looking, [Peter gives him an incredulous look] needed saving.

Name: Rocket
Line: This is the plan? We're gonna hit him with a brick?

Name: Eitri
Line: It's a mold. A king's weapon. Meant to be the greatest in Asgard. In theory, it could even summon the Bifrost.

Name: Thor
Line: Did it have a name?

Name: Eitri
Line: Stormbreaker.

Name: Rocket
Line: That's a bit much.

Name: Thor
Line: So how do we make it?

Name: Eitri
Line: You'll have to restart the forge. Awaken the heart of a dying star.

Name: Thor
Line: Rabbit, fire up the pod.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: The heck happened to this planet? It's eight degrees off its axis. Gravitational pull is all over the place.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Yeah, we got one advantage. He's coming to us. We'll use it. All right, I have a plan. Or at least the beginnings of one. It's pretty simple. We draw him in, pin him down, get what we need. Definitely don't wanna dance with this guy. We just want the gauntlet.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Are you yawning? In the middle of this, while I'm breaking it down? Huh? Did you hear what I said?

Name: Drax
Line: I stopped listening after you said, "We need a plan."

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [To Quill] Okay, Mr. Clean is on his own page.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: See, "not winging it" isn't really what they do.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Uh, what exactly is it that they do?

Name: Mantis
Line: [As fiercely as an 8-week-old kitten] Kick names, take ass.

Name: Drax
Line: Yeah, that's right. [Agrees quietly as he settles into a stance facing the remaining Avengers.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Tony pauses with an expression of deep hopelessness] Alright, just get over here, please. Mr. Lord, can you get your folks to circle up?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: "Mr. Lord." Star-Lord is fine. [Motions to Drax and Mantis,]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: We gotta coalesce. 'Cause if all we come at him with is a plucky attitude....

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Dude, don't call us plucky. We don't know what it means. Alright, we're optimistic, yes. I like your plan. Except it sucks, so let me do the plan, and that way it might be really good. [Peter Parker follows the conversation back and forth like a squash rally.]

Name: Drax
Line: Tell him about the dance-off to save the universe.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: What dance-off?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: It's not a... it's not... it's nothing.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Like in Footloose, the movie?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Excitedly] Exactly like Footloose. Is it still the greatest movie in history?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It never was.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Don't encourage this, alright?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Okay.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: We're getting no help from Flash Gordon here.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Flash Gordon? By the way, that's a compliment. Don't forget, I'm half human. [Quill points at Stark and Parker] So that 50% of me that's stupid? That's 100% you.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Your math is blowing my mind.

Name: Mantis
Line: Excuse me, but... does your friend often do that?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Strange, we alright?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You're back. You're alright.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Hey, what was that?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Panting] I went forward in time to view alternate futures. To see all the possible outcomes of the coming conflict.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: How many did you see?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: How many did we win?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Pause] One.

Name: Thanos
Line: The stone had better be up there... for your sister's sake.

Name: Thanos
Line: You know us?

Name: Thanos
Line: Where's the Soul Stone?

Name: Thanos
Line: I am prepared.

Name: Thanos
Line: How is it you know this place so well?

Name: Thanos
Line: What's this?

Name: Thanos
Line: Tell me what it needs.

Name: Thanos
Line: Of what?

Name: Gamora
Line: All my life, I dreamed of a day... a moment when you would get what you deserved. And I was always so disappointed. But now... you kill and torture... and you call it mercy. The universe has judged you. You asked it for a prize, and it told you no. You failed. And do you wanna know why? Because you love nothing. No one.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Turns to face Gamora with tears in his eyes.]

Name: Gamora
Line: Really? Tears?

Name: Gamora
Line: No! This isn't love!

Name: Thanos
Line: [Thoroughly convicted.] I ignored my destiny once. I cannot do that again. Even for you. [Gamora stares down unseeing for a moment, then up at the resolution on his face. She grabs the red-jeweled dagger from his belt with lightning reflexes, triggers the blades and stabs herself in the stomach... except it's only bubbles.] I'm sorry, little one. [He grabs Gamora by the arm and walks inexorably to the precipice.]

Name: Gamora
Line: No!

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Walking up to the pilot's seat] Drop to 2600, heading 0-3-0.

Name: T'Challa
Line: And what did you imagine?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [To Rhodey] Should we bow?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: [Seriously] Yeah, he's a king.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Seems like I'm always thanking you for something. [Shaking hands with King T'Challa.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: [Mock shocked] What are you doing?

Name: T'Challa
Line: Uh, we don't do that here. [He dissuades Bruce with a motion of his hand; Bruce shoots Rhodey a look, and is answered with a big grin] So how big of an assault can we expect?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Uh, sir, I think you can expect quite a big assault.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: How we looking?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: How you been, Buck?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Right, we had to attach each neuron non-sequentially.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Uncertainly] Because, we didn't think of it.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Can you do it?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: How long?

Name: James Rhodes
Line: [also outside, and now in full War Machine armor watching three more ships burn through the sky] Yeah, don't start celebrating yet, guys. We got more incoming outside the dome.

Name: Vision
Line: [Struggling to sit up and slide off the exam table] It's too late. We need to destroy the stone now.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: [Moving toward Vision] Vision, get your ass back on the table.

Name: T'Challa
Line: We will hold them off. [He, Okoye and the guards head for the door.]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [To Wanda] Wanda, as soon as the stone's out of his head... you blow it to hell.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I will.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Evacuate the city. Engage all defense procedures. [He stops, turns, and points at Steve] And get this man a shield.

Name: Rocket
Line: I don't think you get the scientifics here. These rings are gigantic. You wanna get them moving, you're gonna need something a lot bigger to yank 'em loose.

Name: Thor
Line: Leave that to me.

Name: Rocket
Line: Leave that to you? Buddy, you're in space. All you got is a rope and a--

Name: Thor
Line: [Thor begins to swing the pod around him in a circle. Rocket screams. Thor builds up speed with three good loops then slacks his grip enough to send the pod shooting straight away from Nidavellir, trailing him behind it like a kite tail.] Fire the engines!

Name: Rocket
Line: [Rocket shakes it off and puts the proverbial pedal to the metal.] Nnnyah!

Name: Thor
Line: [As the pod skims over the surface of the next ring out, Thor reaches down and digs one hand into the surface, then both feet, finally getting a foothold against the forward motion of the pod. The ice-like accumulation around the ring axis crackles.] MORE... POWER... RABBIT!

Name: Eitri
Line: Well done, boy.

Name: Thor
Line: That's Nivadellir!

Name: Eitri
Line: Damn it.

Name: Rocket
Line: "Damn it"? What's "damn it"?

Name: Eitri
Line: The mechanism is crippled.

Name: Thor
Line: What?

Name: Eitri
Line: With the iris closed I can't heat the metal.

Name: Thor
Line: How long will it take to heat?

Name: Eitri
Line: A few minutes, maybe more. Why?

Name: Thor
Line: [Standing up on the pod hull] I'm gonna hold it open.

Name: Eitri
Line: That's suicide.

Name: Thor
Line: So is facing Thanos without that ax. [He leaps from the pod to the star's iris.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: How we looking, Bruce?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Leaping jogging along, keeping up with the carriers, and utterly delighted] Yeah, I think I'm getting the hang of it. Wow! It's like being the Hulk without actually-- [he stumbles on a rock, and a carrier goes by, from which Okoye gives him a dubious look. He stands] I'm okay. I'm okay.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: I got two heat signatures breaking through the tree line.

Name: T'Challa
Line: [Clasps wrists with M'Baku] Thank you for standing with us.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Where's your other friend?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: That's not gonna happen.

Name: T'Challa
Line: You are in Wakanda now. Thanos will have nothing but dust and blood.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Not exactly.

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: Looks like we pissed her off.

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Alright, back up, Sam. You're gonna get your wings singed. [He flies over the heaviest concentration of Outriders and drops a barrage of mines, all exploding fantastically.]

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Cap, if these things circle the perimeter and get in behind us... there's nothing between them and Vision.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Grimly] Them we better keep 'em in front of us.

Name: T'Challa
Line: We open the barrier. [Putting his comm to his mouth] On my signal, open North-West Section Seventeen.

Name: T'Challa
Line: On my signal.

Name: T'Challa
Line: WAKANDA FOREVER!!!! [He crosses his arms in the Wakandan salute and closes his Black Panther helmet, charging for the barrier. The heroes and leaders are at the fore of the charge. Halfway to the barrier, the Black Panther shouts into his comm] Now!

Name: T'Challa
Line: [Over his comm] How much longer, Shuri?

Name: T'Challa
Line: You might want to pick up the pace.

Name: Thor
Line: Allfathers, give me strength.

Name: Eitri
Line: You understand, boy? You're about to take the full force of a star. It'll kill you.

Name: Thor
Line: Only if I die. [Takes deep breaths.]

Name: Eitri
Line: [Boggled] Yes. That's what... "killing you" means.

Name: Eitri
Line: Hold it! Hold it, Thor!

Name: Rocket
Line: [Kneeling over Thor] Thor! Say something. Come on. Thor, you okay? [Thor looks far from "okay".]

Name: Rocket
Line: I think he's dying!

Name: Eitri
Line: He needs the ax! Where's the handle? Tree, help me find the handle!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: There’s too many of them! GYAH! AAAAHHHHH!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Opening the Hulkbuster's helm and laughing with joy] AH-hahaha! You guys are so screwed now!

Name: Thor
Line: BRING ME THANOS! [He charges toward the hordes of Outriders, followed by Groot and Rocket, lightning gathering around him until he finally launches himself into the air, lands in the densest concentration of Outriders and makes a crater where they had stood.]

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Sitting on what may have been plaza steps once] Oh, yeah, you're much more of a "Thanos."

Name: Thanos
Line: I take it the Maw is dead. This day extracts a heavy toll. Still, he accomplished his mission.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: You may regret that. He brought you face-to-face with the Master of the Mystic Arts.

Name: Thanos
Line: And where do you think he brought you? [Star-Lord crouches behind wreckage with his weapon ready, behind Thanos and to his left; Spider-Man peeks from above and behind Doctor Strange.]

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Let me guess. Your home?

Name: Thanos
Line: [Smiling reminiscently] It was. And it was beautiful. [Thanos curls his gauntleted fist and activates the Reality Stone to show Strange Titan before it was destroyed -- green lawns, intact buildings, water-filled ponds, strolling citizens, the jack-like structures hovering and connected to the ground-based buildings with beams of energy.] Titan was like most planets. Too many mouths, and not enough to go around. And when we faced extinction, I offered a solution.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Genocide.

Name: Thanos
Line: But at random, dispassionate, fair to rich and poor alike. They called me a madman. And what I predicted came to pass. [He relaxes his fist; the Stone stops glowing and the illusion fades back into the true state of Titan.]

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Sarcastically] Congratulations. You're a prophet.

Name: Thanos
Line: I'm a survivor.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Who wants to murder trillions.

Name: Thanos
Line: With all six stones, I could simply snap my fingers, and they would all cease to exist. I call that... mercy.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Stands] And then what?

Name: Thanos
Line: I finally rest... and watch the sun rise on a grateful universe. The hardest choices require the strongest wills.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [He summons his Mandalas, entering a fighting pose] I think... you'll find... our will... equal to yours.

Name: Thanos
Line: Ours? [He looks up to a see a chunk of wreckage descending rapidly on him, too rapidly to react -- and powered by Iron Man. He is subsequently crushed by it.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Flying in] Piece of cake, Quill.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Triggers his mask and follows] Yeah, if your goal was to piss him off!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Boom!

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Whispers to the Cloak of Levitation] Do not let him close his fist. [The Cloak swoops off Doctor Strange's shoulders and wraps itself tightly around Thanos' armored hand, who starts tugging at this unexpected wrapping.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: Magic! [He punches Thanos in the head and vanishes through a portal to the lower right before reappearing above Thanos] More magic! [He yanks Thanos' head down hard, then leaps into a portal in front of him. He leaps through another portal high and behind Thanos] Magic with a kick! [Delivers a flying kick and falls feet-first into an exit, then appears on his right] Magic with a--

Name: Thanos
Line: Insect!

Name: Thanos
Line: Well, well.

Name: Thanos
Line: It would've been a waste of parts!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [While pulling] Is he under? Don't let up.

Name: Mantis
Line: [Starting to cry] Be quick. He is very strong.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Parker, help! Get over here. [Spider-Man drops his web-line, and hurries to help Tony with the gauntlet] She can't hold him much longer. Let's go.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Flies over to join the others, stands in front of Thanos, tauntingly] I thought you'd be harder to catch. For the record, this was my plan. Not so strong now, huh? Where is Gamora?

Name: Thanos
Line: My Gamora...?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: No, bull-shit. Where is she?

Name: Mantis
Line: [Shocked] He is in anguish.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Good.

Name: Mantis
Line: [Crying] He… he mourns.

Name: Drax
Line: What does this monster have to mourn?

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Pause] What?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Frasps the danger immediately and de-helmets] Okay, Quill, you gotta cool it right now, you understand?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Shouting his pleads desperately] Don't, don't, don't engage, we've almost got this off!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Tell me she's lying. [Enraged] Asshole! Tell me you didn't do it!

Name: Thanos
Line: I... had... to.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [While starting to tear up; quietly] No, you didn't…! No, you didn't…! [He continues to rage and then pistol-whipping Thanos twice in the face, causing Mantis to let go in pain.] NO, YOU DIDN'T!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Quill!

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [To the struggling Star-Lord] Hey, stop! Hey, stop! Stop! Hey, stop! Stop!

Name: Peter Parker
Line: It's coming! It's coming! It's coming! [Getting the fingers completely loose] I got it! I got it.... !

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Seeing Mantis with far too much air under her] Oh, God. [He jumps and wraps his arms and legs around her, extending his spider legs to form a roll cage for a safe landing.]

Name: Rocket
Line: [Having found a clear spot] Come and get some, space dogs! [Another wave of Outriders heads right for the raccoon-oid. The Winter Soldier, having come up behind Rocket, grabs him with his mechanical arm, holds him at arms length and spins 540 degrees, firing his own M-249 at the same time.] Come on, get some, get some! Come on, get some! [The Winter Soldier drops Rocket, who looks up at him with an impressed gleam] How much for the gun?

Name: Rocket
Line: Okay, how much for the arm? [The Winter Soldier just gives him a look and moves off] Oh, I'll get that arm.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Panting] New haircut?

Name: Thor
Line: [Grinning] Notice you've copied my beard.

Name: Thor
Line: By the way, this is a friend of mine. Tree. [Gestures towards Groot with Stormbreaker]

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Formally, but bemused] I am Steve Rogers.

Name: T'Challa
Line: Fall back! Fall back now!

Name: James Rhodes
Line: Focus that fire on the left flank, Sam.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Somebody get to Vision!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: I got him! [Bruce has figured out the Hulkbusters repulsor thrusters and makes a beeline for the android.]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: On my way. [She is clobbered by Proxima Midnight's pommel and rolls down into the large ditch from the Thresher before she can move.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: She's not alone.

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Oh no, oh no you don't. This isn't going to be like New York, pal. This suit's already kicked the crap out of the Hulk-- [Cull Obsidian jumps forward, grabs Bruce's right arm and Bruce in reflex grabs Obsidian's hammer; a jet fires, taking the two of them in a random direction, to the base of a waterfall.]

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Guys! Vision needs backup now! [Obsidian pulls the Hulkbuster up and kicks it in the small of the back.] [Trying to change into the Hulk while fighting Cull Obsidian in the Hulkbuster armor] Hulk. Hulk, I know you like making your entrance at the last second, well, this is it, man. This is the last, last second. [Bruce extends his left hand protectively; Obsidian grabs the armor's hand, chops the shoulder joint with a relatively small axe then does a roll over Bruce's back to leverage snapping off the Hulkbuster's whole arm] Ahhhhh! Hulk! Hulk! HULK!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: Oh, screw you, ya big green asshole! I'll do it myself! [To Obsidian] Come on!

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: See you later, Alligator! [The repulsors fire, taking Cull Obsidian high into the air -- high enough, in fact, to intersect the defense dome. The Hulkbuster arm drags Obsidian against the field to grotesque destructive effect, ending in a very final explosion.] Hulk, we got a lot to figure out, pal.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Get outta here! [He exchanges blows with Glaive, using his arm-shields as offence as well as defense, then turns to Vision again] GO!

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: That was really gross.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [helping him back up] I thought I told you to go.

Name: Vision
Line: We don't trade lives, Captain.

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Webs Mantis] I got you! I got you! [Snags Drax, securing both of them to something not moving] I'm sorry I can't remember anybody's names! [Reels in Star-Lord]

Name: Thanos
Line: You're full of tricks, wizard.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [as Thanos reaches for the Eye of Agamotto] No!

Name: Thanos
Line: [He snaps the Eye off its chain] Yet you never once used your greatest weapon. [He crushes it in his bare hand] A fake. [He throws Doctor Strange hard enough that Doctor Strange's head hits stone and he passes out.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [sounding just about done with the Titan] You throw another moon at me, and I'm gonna to lose it.

Name: Thanos
Line: Stark.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: You know me?

Name: Thanos
Line: I do. You're not the only one cursed with knowledge.

Name: Tony Stark
Line: My only curse is you. [Small rockets pop out of Iron Man's back and launch at Thanos.]

Name: Thanos
Line: Come on!

Name: Thanos
Line: [Panting] All that for a drop of blood.

Name: Thanos
Line: You have my respect, Stark. When I'm done, half of humanity will still be alive. [He lets go, straightens and steps back] I hope they remember you.

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: Stop! [Sitting up and sounding entirely damaged] Spare his life... and I will give you the stone.

Name: Thanos
Line: No tricks. [Doctor Strange shakes his head as Thanos points all four Stones at him instead.]

Name: Tony Stark
Line: Don't...!

Name: Thanos
Line: One to go. [An energy blast hits the gauntlet right in the empty Mind Stone setting, and Thanos grimaces in surprise.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Screaming in incoherent rage, helmet up, firing with both hands and flying straight for Thanos.]

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Standing and de-helmeting] Where is he?!

Name: Peter Quill
Line: [Now fearful instead of furious] Did we just lose?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [To Doctor Strange, sadly, who has given the Time Stone to Thanos] Why would you do that?

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: We're in the Endgame now.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [landing as she finally locates Vision] Are you okay? [Vision flinches in pain before he can answer] What? What is it?

Name: Vision
Line: He's here.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Everyone, on my position. We have incoming. [He is joined by the Black Widow, Falcon, Okoye and the Black Panther in short order.]

Name: Natasha Romanoff
Line: What the hell?

Name: Bruce Banner
Line: [Bruce sees the blue-black clouds of a Space Stone relocation just before Thanos steps forward, and confirms this isn't just another member of the Black Order] Cap. That's him.

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: Eyes up. Stay sharp.

Name: Vision
Line: Wanda. It's time.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: No.

Name: Vision
Line: They can't stop him, Wanda, but we can. Look at me. You have the power to destroy the stone.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: Don't.

Name: Vision
Line: You must do it. Wanda, please. We. Are. Out of time.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: I can't.

Name: Vision
Line: Yes, you can. You can. If he gets the stone, half the universe dies.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: It's not fair.

Name: Vision
Line: It shouldn't be you, but it is. It's all right. You could never hurt me. I just... feel you. [The Scarlet Witch extends a trembling hand and starts beaming her energy at the Mind Stone.]

Name: Vision
Line: [Very softly] It's all right. It's all right. I love you.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Walking closer to the Scarlet Witch] I understand, my child. Better than anyone.

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: [Snarls] You could never.

Name: Thanos
Line: [Reaches down to presume to stroke her hair, as if in comfort] Today, I lost more than you can know. But now is no time to mourn. Now... is no time at all. [He reaches forward, clenching the gauntlet, emerald filigree surrounding his wrist, making a gesture very similar to that Doctor Strange made when activating the Eye of Agamotto. In response, a bead of yellow light starts gathering in on itself as time is reversed and growing in size, solidifying into an intact and conscious Vision]

Name: Wanda Maximoff
Line: No! [She lunges for Vision and is swatted away.]

Name: Thor
Line: [Lands in front of Thanos, who is down on one knee; hatefully.] I told you. You'd die for that! [reffering to the deaths of Loki and Heimdall]

Name: Thanos
Line: [Weakly] You should have... you... [suddenly stronger] You should have gone for the head! [He raises his gauntlet and snaps his fingers.]

Name: Thor
Line: NO!

Name: Thanos
Line: Daughter?

Name: Gamora
Line: Did you do it?

Name: Thanos
Line: Yes.

Name: Gamora
Line: [Beat] What did it cost?

Name: Thanos
Line: [Solemnly] Everything.

Name: Thor
Line: What'd you do? [Angrily] WHAT'D YOU DO?!

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Stumbles into the clearing, holding his left side] Where'd he go? Thor... where'd he go?

Name: T'Challa
Line: [While reaching for a fallen Okoye] Up, General. Up! This is no place to die. [King T'Challa holds out his hand for Okoye. He suddenly disintegrates into ashes and, in anguish, Okoye falls back on the ground. Few seconds later, she gets up herself.]

Name: Rocket
Line: No... no. No. No. No! Groot, no...

Name: James Rhodes
Line: [Searching for Sam, missing him by only a few feet] Sam? [Back to Okoye is is whimpering for her disintegrated king] Sam, where you at?!

Name: Mantis
Line: Something's happening. [She disintegrates into ashes.]

Name: Drax
Line: [To Quill as he dissolves] Quill?

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Staring panicked at the slowly fading Quill] Steady, Quill.

Name: Peter Quill
Line: Aw, man. [Quill also gets disintegrated into ashes]

Name: Stephen Strange
Line: [Calmly turns to Stark] Tony, there was no other way. [He finally gets erased.]

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Realizes he's fading away] Mr. Stark? [Stark stares horrified at Parker,] I don't feel so good...

Name: Tony Stark
Line: [Trying to be calm, his voice shaking as he looks at Peter in terror] You're all right?

Name: Peter Parker
Line: [Stumbling and terrified] I don't know what's -- I don't know what's happening. I don't-- [Parker falls into Stark's arms, clutching him tight while beginning to cry.] I don't wanna go, I don't wanna go, Mr. Stark, please. Please, I don't wanna go. I don't wanna go... [There is a short silence before Peter speaks again] I'm sorry. [Parker disintegrates into ashes in Stark's arms.]

Name: James Rhodes
Line: What is this? What the hell is happening?

Name: Steve Rogers
Line: [Pause] Oh, God.
